* Asking for help with Okular
** Contact
You can contact the Okular team in many ways.

** Mailing list
We have a mailing list to coordinate the Okular development. The mailing list is okular-devel and hosted at kde.org.
You can use it to talk about the development of the core application, but also feedback about existent or new backends is appreciated.

** IRC !!!
We have also an IRC channel where talk. The channel is #okular, on the Freenode network.
Usually some of the Okular developers hang there.
** Forum
If you prefer using a forum you can use the Okular forum inside the bigger KDE Community Forums.
** Bugs and Wishes
Bugs and Wishes should be reported to the KDE bug tracker at http://bugs.kde.org.

